### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

###

### All students
GET http://localhost:3000/api/students

###

### Filter students (pass + search)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/students?status=pass&search=ali

###

### One student by id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/students/1

###

### Create student
POST http://localhost:3000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Hafizullah Khokhar",
  "marks": 78,
  "subject": "Programming Fundamentals"
}

###

### Update student
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/students/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Sara Khan",
  "marks": 66,
  "subject": "Computer Science"
}

###

### Delete student
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/students/4

###

### Dashboard stats
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stats

###

### Invalid payload test
POST http://localhost:3000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "A"
}